## UX During Async Operations

Many operations take time:
- Agent analysis (5-60 seconds)
- Saving to LocalStorage
- Confidence calculations
- Export generation

Users need feedback during these operations.

### Loading State Types

#### 1. Agent Analysis (Long)

\`\`\`
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Devil's Advocate is analyzing your hypothesis...              │
│                                                                 │
│  ████████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  25%                        │
│                                                                 │
│  ⏱️ Typical time: 30-60 seconds                                │
│                                                                 │
│  What's happening:                                              │
│  ✓ Reading your hypothesis                                     │
│  → Identifying assumptions                                      │
│  ○ Formulating challenges                                       │
│  ○ Generating response                                          │
│                                                                 │
│  [Cancel]                                                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
\`\`\`

#### 2. Save Operations (Quick)

Optimistic update with background sync:
\`\`\`typescript
// User clicks save
setState(newValue);  // Immediate UI update
showToast("Saving...");

try {
  await persistToStorage(newValue);
  showToast("Saved ✓", { duration: 1000 });
} catch (error) {
  rollbackState(previousValue);
  showToast("Save failed - try again", { type: 'error' });
}
\`\`\`

#### 3. Page Transitions

Skeleton screens while session loads:
\`\`\`
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Loading session...                                             │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────                      │
│  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░               │
│  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░                        │
│                                                                 │
│  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░       ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░                    │
│  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░       ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░                    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
\`\`\`

### Component Library

\`\`\`typescript
// Skeleton components
<Skeleton width="100%" height={20} />
<Skeleton.Card />
<Skeleton.Form />

// Loading overlays
<LoadingOverlay 
  visible={isLoading}
  message="Analyzing..."
  progress={0.25}
  onCancel={() => cancelOperation()}
/>

// Toast notifications
toast.loading("Saving...");
toast.success("Saved");
toast.error("Failed to save");

// Progress indicators
<AgentProgress 
  agent="devils_advocate"
  steps={['reading', 'analyzing', 'challenging', 'responding']}
  currentStep={1}
/>
\`\`\`

### State Management

\`\`\`typescript
interface AsyncOperationState {
  status: 'idle' | 'loading' | 'success' | 'error';
  progress?: number;
  message?: string;
  startedAt?: Date;
  estimatedDuration?: number;
  cancellable: boolean;
}
\`\`\`

### File Locations
\`\`\`
